{"tid":729163,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝皇馬購法國帝星已達協議 2.72億地震巨購替C.朗拿度","createTime":"2018-07-04T10:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T17:13:03.000Z","uid":147522,"like":45,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a284ba3f31f625fa1c4cd43087935c12f52324","tid":729163,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"　　夏季轉會窗又進入到了沸騰的時節，已經結束世界盃之旅的C.朗拿度又引爆了整個足球圈，關於他加盟祖記的傳聞和消息越來越多，人們也從一開始嗤之以鼻的態度逐漸變得信以為真。<br />\n<br />\n　　《世界體育報》就援引法國記者Baptiste Ripart的消息稱，皇馬已經與法甲豪門巴黎聖日耳門隊達成協議，將以2.72億歐元的價格引進法國天才前鋒麥巴比，消息還稱，這筆巨額的違約金將分4期付清。<br />\n<br />\n　　值得一提的是，這位名叫Baptiste Ripart的法國記者，正是之前率先爆料基沙文留隊以及馬體會購入林馬的記者。"},{"pid":"cff0b1ecfc063919cd5bb2037f9f8ba664386163","tid":729163,"uid":99364,"like":58,"dislike":12,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da2471b577439bff5c4bd5284e1cf54b451e0a2d","tid":729163,"uid":131369,"like":1,"dislike":78,"score":-77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"c朗真係慘要part neymar <br />\n小d eq都屌撚爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f9ce5d77a195c5725db9a7d95f1b2034055f3c","tid":729163,"uid":20924,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"尼馬都2億<br />\n麥巴比無3億都帶唔走"},{"pid":"2c5235e581296a48b067eefa860c8d10475950c8","tid":729163,"uid":47268,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"包皮咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4100570621b205dad88d6b47923f06348b14b8e8","tid":729163,"uid":31887,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"包皮抵買啦 拎硬歐聯"},{"pid":"f4dca9eeb866261bad60b3a640d2a0ce2d6adae2","tid":729163,"uid":39731,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"da2471b577439bff5c4bd5284e1cf